    "glowty-pain": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "pain_text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You already know the feeling — you look in the mirror and your eyes look like you didn’t sleep, even though you did. Or there’s a breakout that showed up overnight, right before the one day you didn’t need it. So you reach for concealer, more than you’d like to, just to feel like you can walk out the door.</p><p>You’ve tried the ice roller that rolled right off your face, the acne cream that left your skin red and angry, the LED mask that takes twenty minutes you don’t have. None of it was really <em>for</em> mornings like this.</p><p><strong>What if the fix took three minutes, not twenty — and actually met your skin where it’s at?</strong></p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "pain_text"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "display_id": false,
        "visibility": "always-display",
        "desktop_content_position": "center",
        "content_alignment": "center",
        "full_width": false,
        "color_scheme": "background-2",
        "padding_top": 52,
        "padding_bottom": 52,
        "custom_colors_background": "#ffffff",
        "custom_gradient_background": "",
        "custom_colors_text": "#2e2a39",
        "custom_colors_solid_button_background": "#dd1d1d",
        "custom_colors_solid_button_text": "#ffffff",
        "custom_colors_outline_button": "#dd1d1d"
      }
    },
    "4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a": {
      "type": "icons-with-content",
      "blocks": {
        "template--21507361800487__4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a-icon-1": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "flare",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "title": "415nm Blue Light",
            "text": "<p>Targeted blue light works on the surface of blemish-prone areas to help calm their appearance.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--21507361800487__4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a-icon-2": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "vibration",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "title": "Gentle Sonic Pulse",
            "text": "<p>Works like a light massage — supporting microcirculation and lymphatic flow, which helps the look of morning puffiness ease up.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--21507361800487__4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a-icon-3": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "thermostat",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "title": "Comfortable Warmth",
            "text": "<p>A low, gentle warmth opens the door for your serum or eye cream to actually absorb, instead of just sitting on top of your skin.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--21507361800487__4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a-heading-1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>Three Actions, One Pass,</strong>",
            "title_highlight_color": "#6d388b",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "template--21507361800487__4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Most tools pick one job. An ice roller cools. A spot cream targets blemishes. A serum tries to sink in on its own. Glowty does what those three things do — but at the same time, in one 3-minute pass, with one pen.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "template--21507361800487__4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a-button-1": {
          "type": "atc_button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Shop Glowty"
          }
        }
      },
