    "glowty-faq": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "glowty_faq_1": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is this actually going to work, or is it another gadget I’ll stop using in two weeks?",
            "icon": "help",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Fair question — most of us have a drawer of things that didn’t stick. The honest answer is that Glowty is built to be used, not admired: it’s three minutes, it’s one device instead of three, and it fits into the routine you already have rather than asking you to build a new one. Consistency is what makes it work, and consistency is what a 3-minute ritual is actually designed for.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "glowty_faq_2": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "My skin is really sensitive and reacts to almost everything. Will this irritate it?",
            "icon": "help",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>This is exactly the skin Glowty was designed around. There are no harsh actives, no exfoliation, no chemical ingredients involved — just light, gentle sonic pulse, and low warmth. If you’re currently avoiding acne creams because of irritation, this is a meaningfully gentler category of approach.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "glowty_faq_3": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How is this different from an LED face mask or a jade roller I already own?",
            "icon": "help",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>An LED mask treats your whole face passively over 10–20 minutes and does one job — light. A jade roller is manual and does one job — light massage. Glowty combines targeted light, sonic pulse, and warmth in one 3-minute pass, so you’re not choosing between speed and effectiveness, or between one tool and the next.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "glowty_faq_4": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How soon will I actually see a difference?",
            "icon": "help",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Skin changes gradually, not overnight — most people notice the puffiness and tired look easing within the first couple of weeks of consistent use, with more visible changes to overall complexion over 4–8 weeks. Think of it less like a quick fix and more like a habit that compounds.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "glowty_faq_5": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is it safe to use every day?",
            "icon": "help",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes — it’s designed for daily use as part of your morning or evening routine. Each session is short and gentle by design, so there’s no downtime, no peeling, and nothing to work around.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
