    "glowty-guarantee": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "g_heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Try It <strong>Without the Risk</strong>",
            "title_highlight_color": "#6d388b",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "g_text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We get it — you’ve been let down by beauty gadgets before, and we’re not asking you to take our word over your own experience. Use Glowty for 30 days as part of your real routine. If it hasn’t earned a place in your mornings, send it back for a full refund, no complicated hoops to jump through.</p><p><strong>You’re not committing to a device — you’re just giving your skin three minutes a day to see what happens.</strong></p>"
          }
        }
      },
